":35696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T02:06:01.000Z","msg":"一套48枝standard 嚟喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n得兩架車16枝，一個target 要3-4枝攔截<br />\n金仔射多兩枝導彈就清倉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98c2e4a596f85ee4f50c2eb30603108834c8c710","tid":264472,"uid":8009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T02:17:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n支共世界第一民主啊"},{"pid":"eefa61fb565166b8da0e716c43a61acddf6dba70","tid":264472,"uid":35347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T02:20:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>對付北韓唯一方法係打鳩佢， 打到佢求和就坐係度傾</blockquote><br />\n 咁樣南韓要做好首爾全滅的準備</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"http://nautilus.org/napsnet/napsnet-special-reports/mind-the-gap-between-rhetoric-and-reality/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnautilus.org%2Fnapsnet%2Fnapsnet-special-reports%2Fmind-the-gap-between-rhetoric-and-reality%2F&d=o1PnGbzvBgrRCns9BvjyqU%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=30ca6a88\" target=\"_blank\">http://nautilus.org/napsnet/napsnet-special-reports/mind-the-gap-between-rhetoric-and-reality/</a><br />\n研究都做過啦<br />\n仲有人信北韓會炸得平首爾<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/40.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36b29d6beb70940b9119ca3e289a3c75f627e73e","tid":264472,"uid":20522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T02:24:16.000Z","msg":"南泡班on9夠膽就叫美國撤軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}